All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Agent
Agent.java This file is part of the project_biu graph representation.
BinOpAgent
BinOpAgent is an agent that performs a binary operation on the last values of two input topics and publishes the result to an output topic.
Config
Config.java This file is part of the project_biu configuration interface.
ConfLoader
ConfLoader is a servlet that handles the uploading of configuration files and builds a graph representation from the uploaded content.
GenericConfig
GenericConfig is a configuration class that loads agents from a specified configuration file.
Graph
Graph is a collection of nodes representing topics and agents.
GraphDisplayer
GraphDisplayer is a servlet that generates an HTML page to visualize the graph structure.
HtmlGraphWriter
HtmlGraphWriter is responsible for generating HTML code that visualizes a graph structure.
HtmlLoader
HtmlLoader is a servlet that serves HTML files from a specified folder.
HTTPServer
HTTPServer.java This file is part of the project_biu HTTP server interface.
IncAgent
IncAgent is an agent that subscribes to a topic, increments the received value by 1, and publishes the result to another topic.
Message
Message.java This file is part of the project_biu graph representation.
MyHTTPServer
MyHTTPServer is a custom HTTP server implementation that listens for incoming HTTP requests, manages servlets for different HTTP commands, and handles client connections in a thread pool.
Node
Node.java This file is part of the project_biu configuration management system.
ParallelAgent
ParallelAgent is an implementation of the Agent interface that processes messages in parallel.
PlusAgent
PlusAgent.java This file is part of the project_biu configuration management system.
RequestParser
RequestParser is a utility class that parses HTTP requests from a BufferedReader.
RequestParser.RequestInfo
Represents the parsed request information.
Servlet
Servlet interface defines the contract for servlets in the project.
TableDisplayer
TableDisplayer is a servlet that generates an HTML table displaying the last values of all topics.
Topic
Represents a topic in the graph system.
TopicDisplayer
TopicDisplayer is a servlet that handles HTTP requests to publish messages to topics and displays the graph and table of topics with their last values.
TopicManagerSingleton
TopicManagerSingleton provides a singleton instance of TopicManager.
TopicManagerSingleton.TopicManager
TopicManager is a singleton class that manages topics and their messages.
